{"tid":2494440,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"其實屌林家謙既人有份搞死香港樂壇","createTime":"2021-04-18T14:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T15:23:30.000Z","uid":119591,"like":140,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7117f380d6388f080241226cbf0137bb1632f423","tid":2494440,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"今晚林家謙攞咁多獎<br />\n次次都要講野真係好撚難<br />\n重點係佢啲歌全部都自己作<br />\n你想佢多謝自己定點？<br />\n一人之境 詞曲編監唱都係自己<br />\n香港近代有邊個屈得過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且佢真係毒撚性格 唔識講野<br />\n無音樂公司 無budget做宣傳 無姜B咁多打手<br />\n今晚佢得到既都係靠自己<br />\n香港樂壇未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家謙：多謝香港人，聽多啲廣東歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都反得落你班連登仔係弱智定食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ab937f4ea379de9553faf522a3392dc8a36eba","tid":2494440,"uid":119591,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"193有果句講嗰句=清泉<br />\n林家謙=屌 無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf9923e3e9e02d839d7bf98c0d93b1b5c21d989","tid":2494440,"uid":4001,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"屌你假假地都講返多謝自己先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1a4db4f2f5080e309c21d0d87b40826312fa31","tid":2494440,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51ab937f4ea379de9553faf522a3392dc8a36eba","tid":2494440,"uid":119591,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"193有果句講嗰句=清泉<br />\n林家謙=屌 無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"變左圓滑先配囉獎"},{"pid":"d6b3c82263d53377ab93f034c6ac7172b1ade3cd","tid":2494440,"uid":375641,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"193 句野對tvb講<br />\n林家謙句野係對viutv 對我地講"},{"pid